content.rendered:
Caramel Monster is an Indica dominant hybrid, her flavorful smooth taste with sweet floral aromas has derived from the lavender family.

She’ll grow to an average height and produce buds with the characteristics of a true Indica plant, they are dense with an alluring green color and orange hairs together with an incredible coat of resin.

The effects she produces kick in fast, overwhelming you with a happy feeling and relaxed state of mind, a perfect state of mind in which you can let your creativity run seriously wild.

Lamb’s Breath is an extremely potent power-strain producing an amazing uplifting feeling and great euphoric high which makes her a wonderful mood booster and an ideal strain to make your day more breath-taking!

She has a pungent cheesy taste with an earthy undertone accompanied by a mild spicy aroma. Lamb’s Breath grows to an average height, her power packed buds are covered with bright green and orange hairs and a lovely coat of resin.

content.rendered:
As the name suggests, You can set yourself up for a delicious dessert like taste. She has a sour and tangy flavor with a heavenly hint of creaminess.

Her structure is notable for her large and colorful flowers; the buds are dense and coated with an amazing amount of resin which gives her a brilliant and very tasteful look.

Her effects will be noticeable almost instantly, giving you a happy, uplifting even euphoric feeling while at the same time allowing you to stay mentally agile enough to be creative.

content.rendered:
This power-packed hybrid is known all across the globe, as it has super powerful potency levels which pack a punch with every hit you take. Due to her super powerful potency levels her effects will be instant and long-lasting, it will give you an instant stress free, happy uplifted feeling. So, take a seat, relax and enjoy your high!

She can be quite a tall lady, a delightful sight with chunky resin coated buds covering her entire body. Her flavor is earthy and has whiffs of coffee and mocha but don’t let these undertones fool you as she also has a pungent sour flavor that will be stuck to your taste buds for a very long time.

yoast_head_json.og_description: This power-packed hybrid is known all across the globe, as it has super powerful potency levels which pack a punch with every hit you take. Due to her super powerful potency levels her effects will be instant and long-lasting, it will give you an instant stress free, happy uplifted feeling. So, take a seat, relax and enjoy your high!  She can be quite a tall lady, a delightful sight with chunky resin coated buds covering her entire body. Her flavor is earthy and has whiffs of coffee and mocha but don’t let these undertones fool you as she also has a pungent sour flavor that will be stuck to your taste buds for a very long time.

content.rendered:
Dark Star x AK-49 is the shining star in our collection, this Indica dominant strain has a delightful earthy and woody taste to it with some sweet undertones.

She’ll grow to an average height and produce green and blue colored buds that are dense and compact. She is coated with a nice amount of resin which makes it a tasteful, mouth-watering beauty to look at.

Her effects will give you an almost instant uplifted happy feeling placing you in a relaxed and joyful mood.

content.rendered:
Vision Kosher is, as the name suggests one seriously “chill” strain and a true blessing to our collection. Not sure if she would pass as kosher in the classical sense of the word and if not, we certainly think she should.

She doesn’t get very tall but she´s full op buds with a dense structure, bright orange hairs and an amazing coat of resin to give her wonderful glistening look.

Her unique but yet very familiar smell and taste makes you wander in a rich earthy and fruitful dimension, she´s known as one of the tastiest smokes around. She can produce staggering levels of potency which will result in a powerful high, an uplifting feeling putting you in a delightful mood.

content.rendered:
Amnesia X Buddha Kush is a perfect crossed strain, she features the best characteristics of both making her a potency rich powerhouse. She has a strong taste, a combo of delicious earthy and citrusy flavors which will stick to your taste buds for quite a while.

Her sativa influences result in her to grow into a tall lady. Her buds are dense and large, coated with a generous amount of resin which gives her a bright and shiny look.

She an ideal mood-enhancer, her effects will produce a happy uplifted feeling almost euphoric, a cerebral high which will boost your creativity for sure.

Nicole x OG is without a doubt one of the most notable strains in our collection, she’s a super-powerful Indica renowned for her impressive resin production.

She doesn’t get very tall but instead will develop into a compact beauty loaded with buds with very dense flowers and a wonderful coat of resin which gives her a dazzling shiny appearance.

Nicole x OG has a delicious berry flavor with a smooth earthy pine undertone and a pleasant forest fruit aroma. She’s an excellent outdoor strain with high yields. The effects of Nicole x OG is very relaxing and will put you in a great mood.

yoast_head_json.title: Nicole x OG - Vision Seeds
yoast_head_json.og_description: Nicole x OG is without a doubt one of the most notable strains in our collection, she’s a super-powerful Indica renowned for her impressive resin production.  She doesn’t get very tall but instead will develop into a compact beauty loaded with buds with very dense flowers and a wonderful coat of resin which gives her a dazzling shiny appearance.  Nicole x OG has a delicious berry flavor with a smooth earthy pine undertone and a pleasant forest fruit aroma. She’s an excellent outdoor strain with high yields. The effects of Nicole x OG is very relaxing and will put you in a great mood.

@graph.description: for a dream catching grow experience!

content.rendered:
Pure Gelato is a wonderful Hybrid. A Cross between Sunset Sherbet and Thin Mint Girl Scout Cookies.

This Hybrid is an absolute potency powerhouse with a rich earthy and fruity taste, her buds tend to be small but will have a dense structure with bright orange hairs and a shining white coat of resin.

Pure Gelato will put you in an amazing happy mood, you’ll feel up-lifted and pleasantly euphoric while at the same time staying in control, mentally agile enough to be creative as well as productive during your daily routine.
